PREREQUENCES:

   1. Installed WiX Toolset
   2. Installed pandoc
   3. Cygwin with autotools installed.

How to create a package:

0. Fix version in Makefile.

1. Prepare sources to install. In order to do it,
either download a release from github (or tag)
or  run 'make prepare' to install version from 
the current snapshot.

2. Prepare a .pdf documents:
     run `make pdfs`
   or if you have prepared pdfs place then into
   H/H-ints.pdf
   and H/H-user.pdf

3. Export path to the WiX toolset

   export PATH=/cygdrive/c/Program\ Files/WiX\ Toolset\ v3.9/bin/:$PATH

4. Run `make`
